Cotswold phoned me, he had spoken to somebody in Page street and they told him if we put Bari on the route plan they would pass it.  I was so annoyed at this. Why couldn't they say that in the first place. The thing that annoyed me most was it is impossib
le to make Brindisi in one shift but they passed it yet all the places we had put on the route plans that could have been reached they rejected.  So that was basically a week's work wasted because of some idiot with a bit of power.
