d at dinner-time and asked if I wanted to go to a barn sale with him so I went.  When we come back from the sale he invited me over for me tea, couldn't refuse it saves me making anything.  I spent the rest of the day with them.
\par 
\par Sun
\par Didn't do a lot today.
  My boss was working outside this morning. It was raining heavily and his pocket in his waterproof jacket filled with water and drowned his phone so I had the phones. He was going out for tea this afternoon so he asked me if I would go to Lockerbie and l
oad a wagon. I went and loaded the wagon and had an early night.
