 not being there because it wasn't my weekend to have him.
\par 
\par Sun
\par It is }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 's birthday this Thursday so I am treating her. I am taking her to Glasgow to see her sister and to go to the SECC to see Westlife as she likes them a lot.
\par I wasn't really looking forward to seeing a b
oy band even though they are good singers. I was pleasantly surprised it was one of the best live shows I have seen, they were really good.  I enjoyed it a lot. The only thing was we didn't get home til 1am and I had to be at work by 8am.
\par 
\par 
\par 
\par }{\b\fs24\insrsid13964281 Diary 16
\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 Mon
\par Tired this morning but just got on with what I had to do.  The livestock is quieting down, the abattoirs have stopped killing hogs and started killing lambs so we will be quiet for a week or two because there isn't a lot of lambs in Cumbria this year.

\par I done all my tipper notes this morning. I was so engrossed it was dinner time before I realised.
\par }{\fs24\insrsid11086707 D}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  was in a meting this afternoon so when the cat's away the mice will play.  I had a look on the internet at houses to give me a bit of an idea of what would be go
od to build.  I ordered some more brochures so we had a good scope of what is available.
\par Tuesday We found out today that DEFRA has revoked the licence allowing markets to have live store sales. We couldn't find out why DEFRA won't give anybody a reason why
.  The first live sale is supposed to be on Friday. There is sheep booked for the first sales. The markets and ourselves have to contact the customers to tell them we are not allowed to pick their sheep up to take them to market.  There was a lot of upset
 people especially when we couldn't give them an explanation why.  DEFRA are good at letting people down then leaving other people to do the explaining and picking up the pieces.
\par We tried all afternoon to get an explanation of DEFRA why they revoked the licence but we would have been as well talking to the sheep we carry.
\par 
\par Weds
\par Still no explanation this morning but we find out that they might grant the licence now.  The sales have already been cancelled so there will be no store sale this week,  We think the
y are playing their usual fame of stalling things for a while. They don't seem to care who they upset along the way. For a supposedly free country we are all being controlled in a way by people who have been given a bit of power which has gone to their he
ads.  About 40 or 50% of this country is involved or linked to the livestock industry, possibly more.  At the moment all of these people are being told how to run their business and what they can or can't do. Is this a free country?  
