\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
\par Mon
\par Busy today, paperwork of the Tippers to do but the livestock side is quiet. It's just the time of year between the hogs finishing and the lambs starting. When I got home tonight with it being quite early, I had tea and started fixing another garage door. 
}{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  was out as well stripping paint off another door. We didn't stop until dark so things are taking shape now.
\par 
