nos and the hours they have worked. It will take 3 2 or 3 weeks to sort that out. They already have all this info 10 times over but now they want it all on hard disc.  I will have to check everything we done against the invoices, put it all together, then
 
put it on one disc. All the work is on one disc and all the invoicing is on another disc.  I think that because there is so many Inquiries going on, they are looking for mistakes so they can portion the blame on other people.  I couldn't do anything with 
it today because I was too busy and I won't get a chance tomorrow because }{\fs24\insrsid11086707 D}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  is away again.
\par 
