\par There was a live sale of cows and calves and breeding heifers at Carlisle today. It was the biggest sale of breeding stock yet. }{\fs24\insrsid11086707 D}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  was away again so it was 
left tome again. Things were quite busy  and two of the lads that work in the yard were off so there was a lot to do.  It was 9pm before I went to Carlisle. I had two wagons to load and it was 12.30 am before I came away.  There was no DEFRA people left a
nd nobody to disinfect the wheels on the way out.
