\par 
\par Fri
\par It's }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
's Gran's birthday tomorrow so we went to Kilmarnock tonight. Her Gran is 77 this year. I was finished at reasonable time tonight - 18.45 so we just got ready and set off.  The weather going up was terr
ible, really heavy rain. I was tired from the night before but I was worse by the time we got there.
\par 
