\par We went out for lunch today with }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 's Gran and Papa, we went to a hotel near Troon where they go every week.  I met a lot of their friends who ask
ed where I was from and what I done for a living.  I had a good conversation with 1 or 2 of them and for a change F&M was never mentioned. It was good they talked about holidays and their families and I enjoyed the conversation (no doom and glom).
