\par }{\fs24\insrsid484382 
\par 
\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 Sun
\par Papa got himself a fresh car last week and asked if I would change the oil fro him as he can't get up and down of
 his knees very easily. I like tinkering about with cars and machinery so it was quite good fun.  I done a few other little jobs on the car as well.  The weather was nice and some of papa's neighbours were out in the garden so papa was back and forward ta
lking to them. I would say Papa enjoyed himself as much as I did.
