\par Weds
\par Wh
en I went  to bed last night I wasn't feeling too well. I woke up about midnight and was sick and had a bad stomach.  When I got up I still wasn't feeling too good but like a silly bugger I went to work because I wanted to finish the work for DEFRA.  When
