 sent me to 2 farms near Dumfries, then into Dumfries mart. AS the morning went on I felt worse, bad stomach and really weary.  I got back about 13.30 and went home.  Normally I would have suffered and stopped at work and carried on. But the
 way I feel at the moment I've lost a lot of interest in the job and also I'm coming up to 40 next year. It's time I started looking after myself rather than putting work first and me second.
