\fs24\insrsid13964281  painted one of the garages but when we had got one done I felt I had done enough so we will see what tomorrow brings.
\par Thursday Back to work this m
orning. Still don't feel right but I feel a lot better than I did.  I spent a lot of the day going through checking all the work we done for DEFRA.  It's strange when you see something written down, how you remember other things that are not written down 
t
