ce run.  The road was quiet and the scenery very good, all the stock out in fields lying in the sun.  Some of these officials from down south should take time and come up here. Then they would maybe appreciate what we stand for.  We have some of the best 
scenery in the country and it is agriculture that keeps it that way.  But it's telling these people and making them understand.  
\par 
\par 
