\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 No work today. Just chilled out. Me and }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  went and got some shopping then done very little.  We just laid about but we really should get on and get this house ready for selling.

