\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 I didn't go into work until 09.00 hrs and I am tired, I was hoping it wouldn't be a late night.  It was busy at work but we got everything done and I got finished for 8.30 pm. It was nice to be able to spend a little time with }{
\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 , she is beginning to think I am just a lodger.
\par 
