\par 
\par }{\b\fs24\insrsid13964281 Friday
\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 I phoned DEFRA today to see if we could move the cows from Stranraer on welfare grounds as they are dairy cattle and one of them has calved.  I was told the cattle can\rquote 
t move until next Friday night at midnight.  When DEFRA introduced the interim measures, animal welfare went out of the window.
