\par I wonder quite a lot if Animal Rights k
new about the rules Defra have imposed what their reaction would be.  They give us a lot of abuse about the way animals are transported but over the last 18 month they have been very quiet.  I just wonder if they  knew about something like these dairy cow
s and how much we try our best for the animals, would they be as hard on DEFRA and SEERAD as they are on us?
