oad I had a job getting in to the farm.  After the cattle were loaded I got stuck coming out.  The farmer had to go and get a tractor to get me out.  After I had delivered them I nipped home and picked }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 up.
