 reassured it was 11.30pm before I got to Mam\rquote s to pick }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  up.  Going to bed.  I\rquote ve had enough of this day.
\par 
\par Sat
\par }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 Brother }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 came and finished off the kitchen this morning.  I just have to put everything back now.  The house is like a bomb site.  I took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 to see his little sister. He was chuffed to bits.  S
he is a lot better today but has a touch of jaundice.  I spent most of the afternoon putting the house back in order and cleaning up.  It looks as if it belongs to somebody now.  Spent the evening at the hospital with }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281  and }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .
\par 
\par Sunday
\par }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 is a lot better today but we have been told that it could be 2 to 6 week before we get her home.  The one thing she has been able to do is to get to see her brother away from the TV.  He switched the telly off half way through a football match to go an
d see his sister.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  came out of hospital for an hour this afternoon.  We went to Mam and Dad\rquote s for dinner.  I took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 back to the hospital then took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  up the road and went back to the hospital to se }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  and }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .

