\fs24\insrsid13964281  but we know she is in the best place to be looked after and the nurses are really good.
\par }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 
\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 Weds
\par Off work today.  I took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  into town to get one or two things that she needed and to get a bit of shopping.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 \rquote 
s Mam and Dad and sister arrived today to see }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  They were over the moon when they saw her especially }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 \rquote s sister.  
\par Thursday
\par We got up this morning and I made breakfast for everyone. After breakfast me and A}{\fs24\insrsid16677158  }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 had a walk to the market to see what trade was like.  A}{\fs24\insrsid16677158  }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
was a bit shocked the prices were very good.  We went back home at lunch time had a cup of coffee then went to the hospital to see }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  A}{\fs24\insrsid16677158  }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
had a cuddle today.  He wouldn\rquote t hold her last night but couldn\rquote t resist it today.  They have decided to stop tonight as well.  I\rquote m glad they are stopping for }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 \rquote 
s sake.  It gives her more time with them rather than a flying visit.  
\par }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 
\par }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 Friday
\par Back to work today.  }{\fs24\insrsid11086707 D}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  is away for the week-end.  It\rquote 
s time there was somebody else trained to look after the office as well as me and him.  If anything happened that meant both of us being off work they would be snookered.  I finished early so I could go and see }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281 .
\par 
\par Sat
\par }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  went to the hospital this morning but I had to go to work so I didn\rquote t get in until this afternoon.  }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
