\par I thought I was up fairly early this morning.  I was going to have al jobs done in the huse and into the hospital in good time.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 phoned and until she phoned me I forgot the clocks had gone forward. I got my jobs done and went to the hospital.  When we got there }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  said she was just waiting for the doctor to come and check }{
\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  and if everything was OK she could go home.  What a great Mother\rquote s Day for }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  It\rquote s just because she\rquote 
s tried so hard and her determination we are getting her home as soon as we are
