\par First day at home with }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  She wasn\rquote t too bad last night, we managed to get a bit of sleep.  She woke at 07.00 this morning }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 fed her then I unplugged the phone and we got to sleep unto 10.30.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 was putting al her new clothes away today. Everybody has been so kind.  We sat down and had a proper meal tonight.  It was so good because we have been living off sandwiches and fast food.
\par 
\par Tuesday
\par I went to work today.  I am going to work this week and have next week off.  I should have stayed at home.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 is coming for Easter holidays next week so I a trying to work it so I can spend time with everybody.  I feel a bit guilty because I should have stayed at home to help }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  It\rquote s difficult to know 
what is best to do so as to please everybody.  I thought about }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  and }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  all day.
\par 
\par Weds
\par We didn\rquote t have a very good night last night.  }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  has got colic so she was up most of the night.  I couldn\rquote t really be bothered with work.  Things are busy.  I\rquote 
ve been out on a wagon all day.  We have drivers on holiday so I am covering driving.  I could have done without it today.  I was tired but it was better than sitting in the office al day.
\par 
\par Thursday
\par Busy day today.  I was leading sheep into Longtown.  I was lucky this morning.  I had three loads to take in and I missed the queues every time I was in.  After I had finished leading into Longtown I took cattle into Carlisle.
\par }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  had a better night last night.  She only woke once through the night so we were able to get some sleep.  She\rquote s really good considering she shouldn\rquote t be here yet.
\par 
\par Friday
\par I took hoggs from Longtown into Sedbergh today that had been up here for wintering and then I took a load into the Lake District.  When you start moving sheep back home after wintering it'\rquote 
 a good sign summer is on the way.  I was rushing all day because I had them  two loads to do and I had to go up the road to collect }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
.  I am pleased I am on holiday next week because I am ready for the break after these last few weeks.
\par 
\par Sat
\par I helped }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 with the housework today and got her a sleep in the afternoon.  With her being o her own this week and up most nights she was tired. So we set to and between us got the housework done.  We didn\rquote t do a lot the rest of the day.
\par 
\par Sun
\par We didn\rquote t do a lot today.  Mam and Dad were in, then my friend Clive then both my brothers and their kids were in.  We didn\rquote t get our tea until 7.30pm.  After tea we got tidied up after the house being full all day, then chilled out with }{
\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281   and }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  for a while. 
\par 
