\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  The weather was that good }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  was outside in her pram.
\par 
\par Tuesday
\par Jobed about at home unto lunch time today then we went to Asda and got some shopping.  It was a nice day again today so me and }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  were outside most of the afternoon.   R}{\fs24\insrsid16677158  }{
\fs24\insrsid13964281 and his daughter came to see }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  this afternoon.  R}{\fs24\insrsid16677158  }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 was telling me the sheep he bought off }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281 \rquote s Dad have had a good lambing and the lambs are doing well.
\par 
\par Weds
\par Me and }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  set
 to today to clean my garage out.  We took everything out of the garage then I stayed to clean it out.  I got a full van load of old wood out.  We took that down to work and put it on the fire.  When we came back I started to bag the rubbish up.
\par 
\par Thursday
\par Mam and Dad came through today. Dad came to help me in the garage.  I already had the van full of rubbish.  We emptied the racking and moved it so that I could add some more to it.  With the rubbish off the racking we filled Dad's trailer.  Once we had go
t sorted we took the rubbish to the tip.  When we got back we replaced the electric cable into the garage as the old one was that rotten it had broken.  My brother called in on his way to work and connected it up.  It\rquote 
s only taken me a year to get electric back into the garage because I haven\rquote t really had the time to do it.
\par 
\par Friday
\par I helped }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  in the house this morning just tidying up and hoovering.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 wants everything right because her Mam is coming tomorrow and staying for a week.  We went shopping this afternoon.  It\rquote s the first time }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 \rquote 
s been out.  Because she was premature we have to be careful when we take her out.  We are not supposed to take her to supermarkets but we went when things were quiet and not too many people about.  She slept the whole time so it didn\rquote 
t make any difference to her.
\par 
\par Saturday
\par I just jobbed about outside this morning.  I had a load of logs delivered yesterday so I stacked them all against the wall so they didn\rquote t take as much space up and so  they could dry up properly.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281  was a little upset.  }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 H}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 er sister is going to pick her Mum up and fetch her down.  We thought they would have been here this morning but }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [sister]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281  was doing other things so they are not coming unto later on this afternoon.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 
 said if we had known we could have gone and got her Mum ourselves.  It turned out not too bad as they arrived about 3.30pm.  }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  was pleased to see them both.
\par 
\par Sunday
\par I spent most of the day in the garage today.  I built a new work bench as the old one was goosed.  In between doing that I was playing football with }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 .  I took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{
\fs24\insrsid13964281  down to my Mam\rquote s tonight.  His 2 cousins are going to stop with Mam for a few days so he has got someone to play with because I\rquote m back to work tomorrow.
\par 
