\par }\pard\plain \qj \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {\fs24\insrsid13964281 I was just having a laze today and I got away with until after lunch then }{
\fs24\insrsid16677158 A}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  came in needing a hand. I don\rquote t mind helping him I enjoy it. It reminds me of what I used to do when I wo
rked on farms. We were sorting out his potatoes planted as he is going to grow some of his own again this year.
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s1\qj \li0\ri0\keepn\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\outlinelevel0\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \b\f1\fs24\lang2057\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp2057\langfenp1033 {\f0\insrsid13964281 Thursday
