 and me looked after }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [new baby]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281 . Seeing as }{\fs24\insrsid16677158 [wife]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  had spent most of her birthday travelling I cooked her a steak for her tea.
