ly well for someone who has smoked for over 40 years. I took }{\fs24\insrsid4859116 [son]}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  back up the road after tea tonight. I don\rquote t like taking him and he doesn\rquote t like going. Its hard and I wish I didn\rquote 
