\par }{\b\fs24\insrsid13964281 Week Number: }{\fs24\insrsid13964281 69
\par Back to work this morning. }{\fs24\insrsid11086707 D}{\fs24\insrsid13964281  went away at 11 am this morning. He was taking C to hospital to have a baby. He phoned in the afternoon, she had a little girl. I didn\rquote t get finished work until 11 p.m. 

