oday. The tippers were all in this afternoon so I got all their loads imputed into the computer. I heard today that DEFRA are going to try and implement the 150km journeys in August and that they are going to all the other regulations as well. Just when t
hings are starting to go well at work again they are going to come in with their bullshit and stop it. The system is working, everybody has got used to it and can live with it and still make a living. Why change a system that works?
